<br>
“Miragul was one of the greatest arch-mages Norrath have ever known. He wasn’t satisfied with training in just one school of magic, so he learned all four, including Necromancy.” Lileah turned to Emeroun. “He was an Erudite, and he didn’t want to die, so as his last act, he took what he knew of the art of Necromancy and turned himself into one of the Undead. Nobody knows for sure, but it’s thought he destroyed his soul in the process.” She frowned and looked at Emeroun. “What does this have to do with Miragul?”<br>
